                   <a href="" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm float-right">Know More</a>
                </div>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card mb-4 text-muted bg-dark home-category">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.themealdb.com/images/category/pasta.png" alt="Card image cap">
                <div class="card-body">
                   <h5 class="card-title text-center">Pasta</h5>
                   <p class="card-text">Pasta (Italian pronunciation: [ˈpasta]) is a staple food of traditional Italian cuisine, with the first reference dating to 1154 in Sicily.</p>
                   <a href="" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm float-right">Know More</a>
                </div>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card mb-4 text-muted bg-dark home-category">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.themealdb.com/images/category/seafood.png" alt="Card image cap">
                <div class="card-body">
                   <h5 class="card-title text-center">Sea Food</h5>
                   <p class="card-text">Seafood is any form of sea life regarded as food by humans. Seafood prominently includes fish and shellfish.</p>
                   <a href="" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm float-right">Know More</a>
                </div>
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="card mb-4 text-muted bg-dark home-category">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="https://www.themealdb.com/images/category/side.png" alt="Card image cap">
                <div class="card-body">
                   <h5 class="card-title text-center">Side</h5>
                   <p class="card-text">A side dish, sometimes referred to as a side order, side item, or simply a side, is a food item that accompanies the entrée or main course at a meal.</p>
