                <div class="card-body">
                   <h5 class="card-title text-center">Starter</h5>
                   <p class="card-text">An entrée (/ˈɑːntreɪ/ /ˈɒntreɪ/ AHN-tray; French: [ɑ̃tʁe]) in modern French table service and that of much of the English-speaking world (apart from the United States and parts of Canada) is a dish served before the main course of a meal; it may be the first dish served, or it may follow a soup or other small dish or dishes.</p>
